        <description>An multi-purpose missile launcher of of People's Liberation Army. The HJ-12 missile can track the target until it hit, but it can not lock the target in close ranged.</description>
        <techLevel>Spacer</techLevel>
        <graphicData>
            <texPath>Things/Weapon/HJ12</texPath>
